Looking for free CS 189, UGBA 102A/103, Chem 3A/B, Chem 4A review sessions?

Scholab is hosting plenty of these review sessions throughout dead week! Seats are limited (~50/session). To reserve your seat, visit https://scholab.com, sign up, and find/join a review session you want to attend! The platform is 100% free to use!

P.S.

We'll also be adding more free review sessions for more courses in the next few days (Econ 2, Bio 1A/B, Math 53/54, EE 16A/B, CS 61A/B).

We also have a plethora of tutors that cover plenty of other subjects (CS 61A/B/C, CS 70, Physics 7A/B, Data 8/100, Math 54/55) ranging from Free, $5, and $10!
